==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: yī yǐn yī zhuó, mò fēi qián dìng

===Proverb===
'''[[一]][[飲]][[一]][[啄]]，[[莫]][[非]][[前]][[定]]'''

# From every single drink to every single bite, there is nothing that is not preordained.

===Alternate forms===
[[一饮一啄，莫非前定]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

